message: My dad been mad at me all day and he said it’s because he had a dream where I came home from school with a nose job
My friends been mad at me all day and they said it’s because they had a dream where I came home from school with lip filler
Well i had a dream where my dad drove our van off a cliff
I googled how to survive a falling off a cliff while we were midair. Apparently all it took was some pillows
